Subject: Permission scans timed out
Description: I am getting the error message "The operation has timed out" on all of my permission scans today.  They scanned just fine on Friday. I checked the logs and there aren't any logs created for today, which makes me think it's something with the communication between the console and the proxy servers, but nothing changed between Friday and today.
Solution_Comment__c:
Issue:
Receiving the message "The operation has timed out" on all permission scans.


Resolution:
Reboot of the Access Analyzer server corrected the issue.
